### SunPhim — doi port neu can (VS Code REST Client / Rider)
@host = http://localhost:5000

### Crawl 1 trang phim moi cap nhat
POST {{host}}/api/crawler/sync?page=1

### Crawl nhieu trang (1 + tiep theo den maxPages)
POST {{host}}/api/crawler/run-now?maxPages=5

### Crawl nhieu trang (chi dem so trang da goi API list)
POST {{host}}/api/crawler/sync/all?maxPages=10

### Xoa het phim + nhap lai N trang
DELETE {{host}}/api/crawler/reset?pages=5&startCrawl=true

### Chi xoa DB, khong crawl
DELETE {{host}}/api/crawler/reset?startCrawl=false
